PMD pre- and post-analysis tools

The files and directories included in this directory are: 

dispVStime/		generates plots for atom's displacement in each frame
			from an initial position as requested by the user
fpt_analysis_files/	calculates fpt for each trajectory and assigns state
			index to them
neb/			creates an input file for NEB calculation on LAMMPS 
vmd/			creates VMD visualisation file for first frame and
			a final frame requested by the user
README			this file
